Package: elastic
Title: General purpose R interface to Elasticsearch
Description: Easy R connector to Elasticsearch, a NoSQL database built on the
    JVM. This library interacts with the Elasticsearch HTTP API, and includes
    tools for interacting with CouchDB iva the River plugin to Elasticsearch.
Version: 0.1.0.99
Date: 2014-09-15
License: MIT + file LICENSE
